1
00:00:00,470 --> 00:00:01,470
(Korea University Hospital)

2
00:00:01,540 --> 00:00:03,240
(Episode 88)

3
00:00:03,310 --> 00:00:04,710
Are you hurting anywhere?

4
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:07,010
No, I feel fine.

5
00:00:07,710 --> 00:00:10,420
He's recovering well,
probably because he's in great shape.

6
00:00:12,850 --> 00:00:13,850
Thank you.

7
00:00:16,450 --> 00:00:18,720
Give Director Ma a call.

8
00:00:19,220 --> 00:00:20,360
She's probably worried.

9
00:00:20,960 --> 00:00:22,890
Wait, Director Ma knows I got hurt?

10
00:00:23,130 --> 00:00:25,930
Of course. She's the one who called us,
that's how we found out.

11
00:00:26,130 --> 00:00:28,770
What were you doing getting mugged
in a place like that?

12
00:00:29,300 --> 00:00:30,900
I swear, if I ever get my hands
on the guys who did this to you,

13
00:00:30,900 --> 00:00:32,370
I won't let them get away with it.
I mean it.

14
00:00:41,210 --> 00:00:43,280
So are you skipping
the whole knocking thing now?

15
00:00:44,120 --> 00:00:46,420
Is this you finally dropping the act?

16
00:00:48,120 --> 00:00:49,320
You win.

17
00:00:50,220 --> 00:00:51,290
What?

18
00:00:51,720 --> 00:00:53,660
I'll marry Kang Jun Ho.

19
00:00:55,330 --> 00:00:59,730
But you'll never get your ultimate prize,
Dream Group.

20
00:00:59,900 --> 00:01:00,930
Don't even dream of it.

21
00:01:01,600 --> 00:01:02,930
We'll see about that.

22
00:01:03,640 --> 00:01:05,600
I guess we'll just have to wait and see.

23
00:01:05,600 --> 00:01:06,840
On one condition.

24
00:01:07,540 --> 00:01:09,470
In exchange for my marrying Kang Jun Ho,

25
00:01:10,110 --> 00:01:13,110
don't you dare touch my family
and the man I love, Baek Ho.

26
00:01:13,750 --> 00:01:14,850
That includes my sister, Seo Rin.

27
00:01:16,510 --> 00:01:18,350
You should have just agreed
from the start.

28
00:01:20,650 --> 00:01:23,190
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

29
00:01:26,190 --> 00:01:28,030
When you finally surrender like this,

30
00:01:28,330 --> 00:01:29,890
do you have any idea
how much more pleasant you are?

31
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:31,800
Seo Rin?

32
00:01:32,160 --> 00:01:35,270
I will throw you
the most magnificent wedding.

33
00:01:36,970 --> 00:01:39,770
Stop with the "Mom" thing.
It gives me the creeps.

34
00:01:39,940 --> 00:01:43,110
Anyway, you're going to be
the most beautiful bride.

35
00:01:47,310 --> 00:01:48,310
Seo Rin.

36
00:01:49,380 --> 00:01:50,480
My daughter.

37
00:01:55,150 --> 00:01:58,090
Go on and gloat all you want,
Chae Hwa Young.

38
00:01:58,690 --> 00:02:00,960
Because soon, I'm going to make you
weep tears of blood.

39
00:02:06,060 --> 00:02:08,670
(Strict Bed Rest)

40
00:02:17,040 --> 00:02:18,810
(Baek Ho)

41
00:02:45,300 --> 00:02:48,370
Excuse me. This man is mine.

42
00:02:49,340 --> 00:02:51,340
Hold on, you've got something right there.

43
00:03:29,610 --> 00:03:31,820
Looks like Baek Ho is in a lot of pain.

44
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,490
What are you doing?

45
00:03:39,820 --> 00:03:43,260
Baek Ho, do you have any idea
how worried I was?

46
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:45,030
You're okay, right?

47
00:03:45,100 --> 00:03:47,900
I'm not okay. It hurts.

48
00:03:47,900 --> 00:03:49,030
Leave me alone.

49
00:03:49,930 --> 00:03:50,940
I'm sorry.

50
00:03:51,570 --> 00:03:54,410
What did the police say?
Did they catch the guy?

51
00:03:54,740 --> 00:03:58,140
- It hurts, so stop talking to me.
- This is so upsetting.

52
00:03:59,080 --> 00:04:01,710
My poor Baek Ho,
you must be in so much pain.

53
00:04:03,380 --> 00:04:04,820
Hong Ju!

54
00:04:08,920 --> 00:04:11,160
Mrs. Han, you must have been so worried.

55
00:04:14,130 --> 00:04:17,200
I brought this for you.

56
00:04:17,460 --> 00:04:18,860
My goodness.

57
00:04:19,100 --> 00:04:22,770
Especially at a time like this,
you need to eat well to stay strong.

58
00:04:22,870 --> 00:04:27,510
Hong Ju, you're just so thoughtful.

59
00:04:27,570 --> 00:04:28,910
And you have such a lovely way
of putting things.

60
00:04:28,970 --> 00:04:32,980
Team Leader Jin, I've told you before,
the only woman for me is Oh Jang Mi.

61
00:04:33,310 --> 00:04:37,180
If you keep making me repeat myself,
things will get awkward between us.

62
00:04:38,180 --> 00:04:42,150
- I think you should leave for today.
- Baek Ho! Don't be so rude to our guest.

63
00:04:43,490 --> 00:04:45,020
Hong Ju, I'm so sorry.

64
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:48,530
It's okay. I'll get going.

65
00:04:53,870 --> 00:04:54,870
Director Ma.

66
00:04:58,240 --> 00:05:00,540
How are you feeling, Lawyer Kang?

67
00:05:00,810 --> 00:05:01,840
When did you get here?

68
00:05:02,340 --> 00:05:03,940
You could have at least said something
when you came in.

69
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:12,480
You're here?
I heard the paramedics called you.

70
00:05:12,980 --> 00:05:16,320
You're my lifesaver, Director Ma.
Thank you.

71
00:05:19,060 --> 00:05:20,490
Come on in, Director Ma.

72
00:05:21,290 --> 00:05:23,930
Thank you so much for saving my Baek Ho.

73
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:26,560
Excuse me a second.

74
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:28,200
Hong Ju.

75
00:05:40,980 --> 00:05:41,980
How are you feeling?

76
00:05:42,710 --> 00:05:43,880
Are you okay?

77
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:46,080
What took so long?
You weren't answering my calls.

78
00:05:46,350 --> 00:05:49,050
Can't you tell I was dying to see you,
Jang Mi?

79
00:05:50,760 --> 00:05:54,530
- You look perfectly fine to me now.
- I'm not, I'm telling you!

80
00:05:55,590 --> 00:05:58,830
Give me a kiss.
Maybe that'll make me feel a bit better?

81
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:02,530
Maybe after you're all better.

82
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:07,410
Did you meet Shin Ae Ran,
Ssangkal's lover?

83
00:06:07,410 --> 00:06:09,840
- What did she say?
- No, I didn't even get to meet her.

84
00:06:10,510 --> 00:06:13,480
Right.
I'll give you Shin Ae Ran's phone number.

85
00:06:14,110 --> 00:06:17,720
I was jumped
right as I was about to meet her.

86
00:06:18,020 --> 00:06:21,220
So what if Shin Ae Ran is secretly working
with Chae Hwa Young,

87
00:06:21,290 --> 00:06:24,560
- and she got you attacked?
- I don't know about all that.

88
00:06:25,220 --> 00:06:28,830
It could be that CEO Chae's people
were tailing Shin Ae Ran...

89
00:06:29,090 --> 00:06:33,260
and they jumped me to scare her off.

90
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:37,200
If CEO Chae knows her whereabouts,
that will be a big problem.

91
00:06:37,770 --> 00:06:40,670
What if we can't get our hands on
what Ssangkal left behind?

92
00:06:40,740 --> 00:06:42,440
Let's just hope it doesn't come to that.

93
00:06:45,580 --> 00:06:48,750
- Does it hurt a lot?
- No. But it's about to.

94
00:06:49,880 --> 00:06:54,390
You have to stay by my side until I leave.
Got it?

95
00:06:54,990 --> 00:06:56,890
- But...
- It's suddenly starting to hurt.

96
00:07:00,320 --> 00:07:01,990
Stop being such a baby.

97
00:07:02,390 --> 00:07:04,630
My gosh, you're such a baby.

98
00:07:19,710 --> 00:07:23,780
The more Baek Ho stands up for me,
the more danger he'll be in.

99
00:07:24,420 --> 00:07:25,780
He can't be with me.

100
00:07:38,500 --> 00:07:40,260
Shin Ae Ran, please pick up.

101
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:42,800
If you don't answer,
you'll be in danger too.

102
00:07:43,170 --> 00:07:45,070
The person you've called is unavailable...

103
00:07:45,070 --> 00:07:47,040
Connecting to voicemail.

104
00:07:51,640 --> 00:07:54,250
Shin Ae Ran, this is Oh Jang Mi.

105
00:07:54,780 --> 00:07:57,550
I heard Baek Ho was hurt
on his way to meet you.

106
00:07:57,850 --> 00:08:00,890
Please meet with me.
If you keep running away like this,

107
00:08:01,150 --> 00:08:03,190
your life could be in danger too.

108
00:08:03,790 --> 00:08:06,020
Please call me back. I'll be waiting.

109
00:08:19,640 --> 00:08:22,240
Seo Rin, why the long face?

110
00:08:23,140 --> 00:08:24,380
Is something on your mind these days?

111
00:08:25,210 --> 00:08:28,810
Goodness,
my little darling looks so troubled.

112
00:08:29,910 --> 00:08:32,020
Am I really that pretty in your eyes,
Grandpa?

113
00:08:32,880 --> 00:08:35,490
Just watching you breathe, my sweet girl,

114
00:08:35,620 --> 00:08:39,260
makes me happier than anything.

115
00:08:40,990 --> 00:08:43,860
Then why are you trying to marry me off
to a man I don't like?

116
00:08:45,130 --> 00:08:47,270
Do you hate the idea that much?

117
00:08:47,670 --> 00:08:50,100
You say you're happy
just having me by your side,

118
00:08:50,170 --> 00:08:52,470
but you keep trying to marry me off.

119
00:08:53,800 --> 00:08:54,810
Seo Rin.

120
00:08:55,940 --> 00:08:57,610
This old man...

121
00:08:58,910 --> 00:09:02,080
wishes he could stay by your side forever.

122
00:09:02,710 --> 00:09:04,150
But that's not possible, is it?

123
00:09:04,820 --> 00:09:07,920
I need someone to protect you.

124
00:09:09,250 --> 00:09:13,390
I'm not going to be around forever,

125
00:09:14,460 --> 00:09:18,360
so how could I rest in peace
leaving you all alone in this cruel world?

126
00:09:19,430 --> 00:09:20,500
Grandpa.

127
00:09:21,370 --> 00:09:22,670
That's why...

128
00:09:23,300 --> 00:09:25,770
I need a good man to protect you.

129
00:09:28,640 --> 00:09:31,410
Do you really hate the idea
of marriage that much?

130
00:09:32,880 --> 00:09:35,250
No, that's not it.

131
00:09:35,250 --> 00:09:36,880
I'll marry Jun Ho.

132
00:09:38,620 --> 00:09:40,850
- Are you serious?
- Yes.

133
00:09:41,490 --> 00:09:44,690
Just like you said,
I've started to see Jun Ho differently.

134
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:47,960
You know that I'm so fickle.

135
00:09:51,230 --> 00:09:53,660
Yes! That's my girl!

136
00:09:54,070 --> 00:09:55,330
You did the right thing, Seo Rin.

137
00:10:01,940 --> 00:10:03,740
Hwa Young. Hong Ju.

138
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:08,480
Seo Rin has decided
to marry General Manager Kang.

139
00:10:08,550 --> 00:10:11,650
What? Seo Rin is going to marry Jun Ho?

140
00:10:12,150 --> 00:10:13,820
Hwa Young, congratulations.

141
00:10:14,090 --> 00:10:18,090
We couldn't be happier about Seo Rin
and General Manager Kang's wedding!

142
00:10:24,230 --> 00:10:28,030
What are you pouting for?
Once Seo Rin gets married, you're next.

143
00:10:28,430 --> 00:10:32,100
- Didn't we push her to marry him?
- Whatever.

144
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:34,940
What does Baek Ho even see in Oh Jang Mi?

145
00:10:35,410 --> 00:10:38,810
And Ma Seo Rin, too.
If she was going to marry Jun Ho anyway,

146
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:42,610
- why lead Baek Ho on all this time?
- Unbelievable.

147
00:10:47,020 --> 00:10:48,620
Hello, Tae Pyung.

148
00:10:49,190 --> 00:10:51,260
What a surprise to hear from you.
What's up?

149
00:10:51,320 --> 00:10:53,120
I made some sikhye...

150
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:55,860
and was hoping to drop some off for you
and the Chairman tomorrow.

151
00:10:56,090 --> 00:11:00,160
What a shame.
I'll be out all day tomorrow.

152
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:05,270
I'll be helping Seo Rin with her wedding,
so I doubt I'll have time to see you.

153
00:11:05,500 --> 00:11:06,570
The Chairman's granddaughter...

154
00:11:07,610 --> 00:11:09,840
Director Ma Seo Rin is getting married?

155
00:11:10,070 --> 00:11:14,410
Of course. She's marrying
General Manager Kang Jun Ho.

156
00:11:14,550 --> 00:11:17,820
- Oh, I see.
- I'll drop by.

157
00:11:18,150 --> 00:11:19,420
Thanks, Tae Pyung.

158
00:11:24,590 --> 00:11:26,060
Jang Mi is getting married?

159
00:11:27,090 --> 00:11:28,230
What?

160
00:11:29,190 --> 00:11:31,060
Jang Mi is getting married.

161
00:11:31,900 --> 00:11:33,300
Jang Mi is happy.

162
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:37,100
- Jang Mi is marrying Baek Ho.
- No, Mom.

163
00:11:37,700 --> 00:11:39,370
Jang Mi isn't marrying Baek Ho.

164
00:11:41,040 --> 00:11:43,840
- What's Baek Ho going to do?
- What?

165
00:11:44,740 --> 00:11:46,710
That can't be right.

166
00:11:47,280 --> 00:11:48,410
I like Baek Ho.

167
00:11:49,180 --> 00:11:53,480
- Jang Mi must marry Baek Ho.
- Mom, listen,

168
00:11:54,020 --> 00:11:55,120
What are we going to do about Jang Mi?

169
00:11:56,190 --> 00:11:57,920
She's going to marry Baek Ho's brother,
of all people.

170
00:11:58,460 --> 00:11:59,460
How does this make any sense?

171
00:12:03,960 --> 00:12:05,200
You said you had something to tell me?

172
00:12:05,700 --> 00:12:06,700
I...

173
00:12:07,570 --> 00:12:09,370
I've decided to marry you, Jun Ho.

174
00:12:11,500 --> 00:12:13,140
I'm a bit confused now.

175
00:12:13,800 --> 00:12:15,310
The person sitting in front of me...

176
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:17,040
is Oh Jang Mi, right?

177
00:12:17,480 --> 00:12:19,880
That's right. I'm Oh Jang Mi.

178
00:12:21,050 --> 00:12:22,150
Then what about Baek Ho?

179
00:12:22,850 --> 00:12:25,780
Weren't you and Baek Ho in love
for a long time?

180
00:12:26,020 --> 00:12:27,420
How do you feel about it, Jun Ho?

181
00:12:28,250 --> 00:12:31,590
Do you no longer want to get married
because I'm Oh Jang Mi and not Ma Seo Rin?

182
00:12:31,990 --> 00:12:32,990
Or...

183
00:12:33,620 --> 00:12:36,230
is it because I know your birth mother
is CEO Chae,

184
00:12:36,830 --> 00:12:38,600
and I know everything about her,

185
00:12:39,130 --> 00:12:41,000
that you're uncomfortable marrying me?

186
00:12:42,630 --> 00:12:43,630
Or if it's not that,

187
00:12:44,240 --> 00:12:45,370
are you hesitating out of loyalty...

188
00:12:46,370 --> 00:12:47,970
to Baek Ho?

189
00:12:48,540 --> 00:12:49,540
For me,

190
00:12:49,910 --> 00:12:52,240
more than anything, I'm curious
about your change of heart, Jang Mi.

191
00:12:53,310 --> 00:12:57,150
You told me what CEO Chae did
to your family.

192
00:12:57,720 --> 00:12:59,820
Knowing all of that,
you still want to marry me?

193
00:13:02,220 --> 00:13:05,120
Are you planning to use me as a pawn?

194
00:13:05,490 --> 00:13:06,490
You're right.

195
00:13:07,260 --> 00:13:08,490
Even now,

196
00:13:09,160 --> 00:13:10,260
I'm still in love with Baek Ho.

197
00:13:11,630 --> 00:13:12,730
And as you already know,

198
00:13:13,260 --> 00:13:15,370
my grudge against CEO Chae runs deep.

199
00:13:16,130 --> 00:13:17,300
I'm not going to lie to you.

200
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:20,500
Grandfather wants me to marry you.

201
00:13:21,240 --> 00:13:22,910
I want to honor his wishes.

202
00:13:23,540 --> 00:13:24,540
Also...

203
00:13:25,480 --> 00:13:28,910
Grandfather doesn't know a thing
about CEO Chae.

204
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:32,050
So the choice is yours, Jun Ho.

205
00:13:32,750 --> 00:13:34,190
I'll give you some time to think.

206
00:13:35,820 --> 00:13:38,590
If you're confident that you can make me
fall in love with you,

207
00:13:39,090 --> 00:13:40,560
then go ahead and marry me.

208
00:13:41,490 --> 00:13:43,060
But if you don't have that confidence,

209
00:13:44,400 --> 00:13:46,060
and you'd rather send me back...

210
00:13:47,060 --> 00:13:48,670
to Baek Ho, the man I love,

211
00:13:50,070 --> 00:13:51,570
then you should call off this marriage.

212
00:13:52,470 --> 00:13:55,410
This marriage is up to you.

213
00:14:14,090 --> 00:14:17,190
If you're confident that you can make me
fall in love with you,

214
00:14:17,730 --> 00:14:19,330
then go ahead and marry me.

215
00:14:20,330 --> 00:14:21,900
But if you don't have that confidence,

216
00:14:22,600 --> 00:14:24,270
and you'd rather send me back...

217
00:14:24,800 --> 00:14:26,440
to Baek Ho, the man I love,

218
00:14:27,040 --> 00:14:28,470
then you should call off this marriage.

219
00:14:50,330 --> 00:14:51,330
Baek Ho.

220
00:14:52,430 --> 00:14:53,830
My mind is already made up.

221
00:14:54,630 --> 00:14:56,300
I have to make Oh Jang Mi mine.

222
00:14:58,270 --> 00:15:00,300
No matter what anyone says,
I won't give up on her.

223
00:15:03,410 --> 00:15:04,780
I'm going to fight for my love.

224
00:15:14,650 --> 00:15:15,650
Jang Mi.

225
00:15:16,890 --> 00:15:18,660
I heard you were going to
marry Baek Ho's brother?

226
00:15:19,160 --> 00:15:21,890
- How did you know?
- Is that what's important right now?

227
00:15:22,560 --> 00:15:25,000
What about Baek Ho?
Why are you suddenly marrying Kang Jun Ho?

228
00:15:25,100 --> 00:15:26,100
I've already made up my mind.

229
00:15:27,130 --> 00:15:29,370
It's the only way I can
get revenge on Chae Hwa Young.

230
00:15:30,130 --> 00:15:32,000
As long as I can make Chae Hwa Young pay,

231
00:15:32,700 --> 00:15:33,900
I don't care what happens to me.

232
00:15:47,920 --> 00:15:49,020
Jang Mi!

233
00:15:50,020 --> 00:15:51,690
No, don't do this.

234
00:15:52,220 --> 00:15:54,090
I get what you're trying to do,

235
00:15:54,730 --> 00:15:57,590
but what's the point of getting revenge
if it means throwing your life away?

236
00:15:57,660 --> 00:15:59,400
I've thought long and hard about this.

237
00:15:59,530 --> 00:16:01,730
Revenge is supposed to
bring you peace of mind.

238
00:16:02,300 --> 00:16:03,830
Is it revenge
to make yourself miserable...

239
00:16:03,830 --> 00:16:05,500
- by leaving Baek Ho?
- Tae Pyung!

240
00:16:05,500 --> 00:16:06,740
What about Baek Ho?

241
00:16:07,740 --> 00:16:09,210
After you've broken his heart,

242
00:16:09,570 --> 00:16:11,480
what do you hope to accomplish
by marrying Kang Jun Ho?

243
00:16:12,210 --> 00:16:13,540
I am completely against this marriage.

244
00:16:14,180 --> 00:16:16,380
- I can't let you do this.
- You know...

245
00:16:16,780 --> 00:16:19,420
what Chae Hwa Young did to Mom.
Look at what's happening now.

246
00:16:19,550 --> 00:16:20,750
She completely trashed the store.

247
00:16:22,490 --> 00:16:23,490
And because of me,

248
00:16:24,250 --> 00:16:26,660
- Baek Ho almost died.
- And so?

249
00:16:27,620 --> 00:16:29,260
Your solution is
to make yourself miserable?

250
00:16:29,660 --> 00:16:32,060
Are you going to sacrifice yourself
to save us all?

251
00:16:32,330 --> 00:16:34,030
That's definitely not the answer.

252
00:16:34,630 --> 00:16:36,100
I can't let you do this.

253
00:16:36,170 --> 00:16:39,140
Chae Hwa Young used the people I love
as pawns to get back at me,

254
00:16:39,800 --> 00:16:43,070
I'm going to take
what she treasures most...

255
00:16:43,440 --> 00:16:44,610
and what she holds dearest.

256
00:16:45,280 --> 00:16:47,340
I'll take it away from her forever.

257
00:16:48,580 --> 00:16:49,580
That's...

258
00:16:50,050 --> 00:16:52,450
the way to inflict the worst revenge
on Chae Hwa Young.

259
00:16:52,650 --> 00:16:53,680
What are you talking about?

260
00:16:54,690 --> 00:16:57,520
Chae Hwa Young has someone
she cherishes most?

261
00:16:57,650 --> 00:16:59,460
Yes, that's Kang Jun Ho.

262
00:17:00,660 --> 00:17:01,760
He's Chae Hwa Young's son.

263
00:17:02,290 --> 00:17:03,290
What?

264
00:17:04,660 --> 00:17:05,660
Are you saying Baek Ho's brother,

265
00:17:06,460 --> 00:17:08,770
Kang Jun Ho is Chae Hwa Young's son?

266
00:17:10,430 --> 00:17:13,000
- How is that possible?
- I'm going to make Kang Jun Ho mine.

267
00:17:13,770 --> 00:17:17,940
And I'm going to make Chae Hwa Young
kneel before me and beg for mercy.

268
00:17:18,380 --> 00:17:20,840
I'll make her grovel and plead
for me to give him back.

269
00:17:21,450 --> 00:17:24,350
That's the only way
to protect the people I love...

270
00:17:24,850 --> 00:17:26,920
and to hurt Chae Hwa Young the most.

271
00:17:27,750 --> 00:17:28,750
So please,

272
00:17:30,550 --> 00:17:31,560
don't try to stop me.

273
00:17:33,490 --> 00:17:36,660
- Here you go.
- Mom,

274
00:17:36,830 --> 00:17:40,000
Slow down.
How can I eat if you're stuffing my mouth?

275
00:17:40,100 --> 00:17:42,470
I just want you to eat up
and get better soon.

276
00:17:42,470 --> 00:17:44,500
- Here.
- I told you I'm all better now.

277
00:17:50,370 --> 00:17:51,540
Why do you look like you're about to cry?

278
00:17:53,780 --> 00:17:55,010
When you were unconscious...

279
00:17:55,750 --> 00:17:57,410
and I didn't know if you'd wake up,

280
00:17:58,680 --> 00:18:01,690
do you have any idea
how terrified I was that I'd lose you?

281
00:18:02,850 --> 00:18:05,120
My mom's such a crybaby.

282
00:18:05,690 --> 00:18:09,990
I'm Kang Baek Ho.
There's no way I'd go down that easily.

283
00:18:10,230 --> 00:18:11,530
I'm your son, after all.

284
00:18:12,960 --> 00:18:14,130
That's right. My son.

285
00:18:15,030 --> 00:18:16,270
You are my son.

286
00:18:16,830 --> 00:18:18,500
No matter what anyone says, you're my son.

287
00:18:20,470 --> 00:18:21,770
My precious boy.

288
00:18:21,870 --> 00:18:23,970
What's with the sudden drama?

289
00:18:25,040 --> 00:18:26,280
Here.

290
00:18:26,440 --> 00:18:27,510
Open wide.

291
00:18:41,690 --> 00:18:45,700
Grandma, what's that?
Where did you get that rattle?

292
00:18:46,560 --> 00:18:50,630
This is Suk Hee's.
I can't even let you have it, Bo Ra.

293
00:18:51,370 --> 00:18:53,000
What's so special about it?

294
00:18:54,910 --> 00:18:57,110
It's precious. It's Suk Hee's.

295
00:19:03,450 --> 00:19:04,650
Shut your mouth, you punk!

296
00:19:06,020 --> 00:19:08,650
Do you have any idea
how patient I've been with you?

297
00:19:09,320 --> 00:19:12,360
I treated you with respect,
and it went straight to your head.

298
00:19:12,660 --> 00:19:13,660
Hey.

299
00:19:13,960 --> 00:19:16,990
You really think CEO Chae is in love
with a piece of trash like you?

300
00:19:17,630 --> 00:19:19,530
Snap out of it, you punk!

301
00:19:21,030 --> 00:19:24,100
You really think CEO Chae is in love
with a piece of trash like you?

302
00:19:24,300 --> 00:19:26,200
No. It can't be.

303
00:19:32,640 --> 00:19:33,740
Lawyer Han.

304
00:19:34,380 --> 00:19:37,080
Or I guess we're about to be in-laws,
aren't we?

305
00:19:38,780 --> 00:19:41,620
This is so lovely. Please, have a seat.

306
00:19:41,920 --> 00:19:42,920
Thank you.

307
00:19:49,190 --> 00:19:53,630
Seo Rin is also thrilled
about marrying Jun Ho.

308
00:19:54,130 --> 00:19:56,500
Is she? I'm so glad to hear that.

309
00:19:56,570 --> 00:20:00,040
They wanted to plan their own wedding,
but I told them that just wouldn't do.

310
00:20:00,370 --> 00:20:04,310
I said we couldn't do a half-hearted job
when our first child is getting married.

311
00:20:04,370 --> 00:20:05,780
I gave them a stern talking-to.

312
00:20:06,380 --> 00:20:08,110
Of course. You're absolutely right.

313
00:20:09,610 --> 00:20:13,350
I guess my Jun Ho
is really getting married.

314
00:20:13,920 --> 00:20:16,750
My father would like them
to hurry with the wedding.

315
00:20:17,120 --> 00:20:19,920
And since the kids
seem to have agreed to it as well,

316
00:20:20,290 --> 00:20:22,690
it's up to us
to handle the wedding arrangements.

317
00:20:23,190 --> 00:20:24,860
I'm so glad you came, my dear in-law.

318
00:20:25,430 --> 00:20:26,460
Are we there already?

319
00:20:27,930 --> 00:20:30,600
That has a very nice ring to it,
my dear in-law.

320
00:20:36,740 --> 00:20:39,740
What's all this talk
about getting them married?

321
00:20:40,480 --> 00:20:42,410
Professor Kang, I didn't realize
you were in your room.

322
00:20:44,110 --> 00:20:45,950
What is wrong with you? How rude.

323
00:20:46,280 --> 00:20:49,120
You said you were sick.
Why are you out here spouting nonsense?

324
00:20:49,620 --> 00:20:51,720
- Get back inside now.
- No, let go of me.

325
00:20:53,090 --> 00:20:56,690
I will not let my Jun Ho
marry into your family.

326
00:20:57,160 --> 00:20:59,830
You seem quite unwell.

327
00:21:00,660 --> 00:21:02,800
I understand the wedding preparations
have been agreed upon between us,

328
00:21:02,800 --> 00:21:03,800
so I'll be going now.

329
00:21:03,930 --> 00:21:07,070
No, please.
At least stay for a cup of tea.

330
00:21:07,140 --> 00:21:09,940
No, that's all right.
I have too much work. I should go.

331
00:21:10,110 --> 00:21:11,780
I'm so sorry.

332
00:21:12,080 --> 00:21:14,980
He's not well,
so please, try to understand.

333
00:21:15,450 --> 00:21:16,450
Goodbye then.

334
00:21:16,950 --> 00:21:17,950
Bye.

335
00:21:19,650 --> 00:21:22,650
I mean what I say!
And don't you forget it!

336
00:21:24,250 --> 00:21:25,690
Are you out of your mind?

337
00:21:26,220 --> 00:21:29,160
Why would you burst in out of nowhere
and ruin everything?

338
00:21:29,490 --> 00:21:31,230
Why do you always do this?

339
00:21:31,860 --> 00:21:32,930
Good grief.

340
00:21:41,770 --> 00:21:42,770
Seo Rin.

341
00:21:43,340 --> 00:21:45,910
I was just about to call you.
Perfect timing.

342
00:21:47,910 --> 00:21:50,150
We need to set your wedding date
with General Manager Kang.

343
00:21:50,450 --> 00:21:51,580
You sound thrilled.

344
00:21:52,880 --> 00:21:54,990
There's something I need to confirm first.

345
00:21:55,820 --> 00:21:58,990
I need to see for myself
that Seo Rin is safe.

346
00:22:00,090 --> 00:22:02,530
- What?
- Why? It's a fair request, isn't it?

347
00:22:03,260 --> 00:22:05,300
For all I know,
you could have gotten rid of Seo Rin...

348
00:22:05,360 --> 00:22:06,930
and be putting on this whole sickening act
in front of me.

349
00:22:07,400 --> 00:22:09,400
You're definitely the type of person
who would.

350
00:22:10,300 --> 00:22:11,370
Show me proof that she's okay.

351
00:22:12,870 --> 00:22:14,940
Is that how little
you trust your own mother?

352
00:22:17,640 --> 00:22:18,680
Here.

353
00:22:22,010 --> 00:22:23,810
I'll send it to you if you insist.

354
00:22:27,880 --> 00:22:31,690
But don't even think
about using that photo to track her down.

355
00:22:32,020 --> 00:22:33,990
She's somewhere you'll never find her.

356
00:22:34,190 --> 00:22:36,430
So you're going to hold Seo Rin hostage
until the very end?

357
00:22:37,060 --> 00:22:38,130
How low and despicable.

358
00:22:38,160 --> 00:22:40,330
You've got quite a mouth on you.

359
00:22:41,060 --> 00:22:44,570
Then again, you must be furious right now,
so I'll let it slide.

360
00:22:45,540 --> 00:22:47,900
You're becoming more and more like me.

361
00:22:48,610 --> 00:22:50,840
Or maybe just similar in some ways.

362
00:22:51,640 --> 00:22:54,640
In how we both desperately fight
to protect what's ours.

363
00:22:54,880 --> 00:22:55,910
Chae Hwa Young.

364
00:22:56,210 --> 00:23:00,580
You don't seem to know your own worth.
Let me spell it out for you.

365
00:23:01,120 --> 00:23:02,490
Go on, let's hear it.

366
00:23:02,490 --> 00:23:05,160
You're a piece of filth
worse than garbage.

367
00:23:05,560 --> 00:23:07,860
Don't you dare think you've won,
you piece of trash.

368
00:23:08,290 --> 00:23:09,290
What did you say?

369
00:23:10,730 --> 00:23:12,930
How dare you!
I let you speak and this is what you say?

370
00:23:21,300 --> 00:23:22,710
What do you think you're doing?

371
00:23:25,280 --> 00:23:28,180
Don't tell me
this was also part of your plan.

372
00:23:28,380 --> 00:23:30,850
We can't discuss our marriage without him,
can we?

373
00:23:31,110 --> 00:23:32,120
Mother.

374
00:23:38,260 --> 00:23:40,390
What could you have possibly done
to deserve this?

375
00:23:42,760 --> 00:23:44,130
How could you do this to her?

376
00:23:45,030 --> 00:23:47,800
I'm okay. Please, don't raise your voice.

377
00:23:48,900 --> 00:23:51,300
If any of the staff see this,
it'll put her in an awkward position.

378
00:23:53,070 --> 00:23:54,810
You've turned into quite the vixen.

379
00:23:55,240 --> 00:23:57,840
- Stop with the phony act.
- That's enough.

380
00:23:59,580 --> 00:24:00,580
Let's go.

381
00:24:01,010 --> 00:24:02,750
If this is about our marriage,
we can discuss it privately.

382
00:24:05,450 --> 00:24:09,420
Ma'am, she may be your daughter,
but she's the woman I love.

383
00:24:10,450 --> 00:24:12,490
I won't have you disrespecting her
like this again.

384
00:24:13,060 --> 00:24:16,490
If you ever pull a stunt like this again,
I won't stand for it.

385
00:24:16,990 --> 00:24:19,130
- General Manager Kang.
- Let's go.

386
00:24:25,970 --> 00:24:27,300
That little!

387
00:24:32,310 --> 00:24:33,610
Didn't you sleep well?

388
00:24:34,240 --> 00:24:35,580
You look so exhausted.

389
00:24:38,450 --> 00:24:39,450
Here.

390
00:24:39,780 --> 00:24:41,420
It's ginger honey tea.
It's good for relieving fatigue.

391
00:24:44,890 --> 00:24:46,020
Hold on a second.

392
00:24:55,600 --> 00:24:58,540
As expected from a former chef,
what a performance.

393
00:25:00,900 --> 00:25:02,540
Of all the spices,

394
00:25:02,910 --> 00:25:04,440
cinnamon has a scent
that helps you hold onto memories.

395
00:25:06,680 --> 00:25:08,350
And now, I want to remember...

396
00:25:08,910 --> 00:25:10,280
what you're about to say to me forever,
Seo Rin.

397
00:25:10,810 --> 00:25:11,920
You've got it backwards.

398
00:25:12,920 --> 00:25:16,690
You want to remember my reaction forever
to what you're about to say.

399
00:25:18,390 --> 00:25:19,720
The choice I gave you...

400
00:25:21,120 --> 00:25:22,460
Have you made your decision?

401
00:25:23,530 --> 00:25:24,530
I have.

402
00:25:25,130 --> 00:25:28,130
Perhaps you already knew the answer
when you gave me that choice, Jang Mi.

403
00:25:29,830 --> 00:25:30,900
So that means...

404
00:25:32,570 --> 00:25:35,070
I'm confident I can make you
fall in love with me, Jang Mi.

405
00:25:36,210 --> 00:25:37,410
Please, marry me.

406
00:25:37,940 --> 00:25:39,010
You're choosing...

407
00:25:39,880 --> 00:25:41,750
to betray your brother, Baek Ho?

408
00:25:42,210 --> 00:25:43,210
No.

409
00:25:44,050 --> 00:25:45,780
I'm choosing to fight for my love.

410
00:25:46,380 --> 00:25:50,290
Then, you're okay with me just using you?

411
00:25:52,960 --> 00:25:55,590
I fell in love with you as Ma Seo Rin.

412
00:25:56,930 --> 00:25:58,960
But now, you tell me you're Oh Jang Mi.

413
00:26:01,130 --> 00:26:02,670
The Ma Seo Rin that I knew...

414
00:26:03,270 --> 00:26:04,900
and the Oh Jang Mi sitting before me now,

415
00:26:05,540 --> 00:26:07,100
they're the same person to me.

416
00:26:07,800 --> 00:26:10,270
It was Oh Jang Mi
whom I fell in love with all along.

417
00:26:14,780 --> 00:26:16,050
Now it's your turn, Jang Mi.

418
00:26:16,750 --> 00:26:19,780
Give up on Baek Ho, and marry me.

419
00:26:20,650 --> 00:26:23,420
I'll make you fall in love with me,
so just trust me.

420
00:26:23,750 --> 00:26:27,120
But you must know
what I intend to do to CEO Chae.

421
00:26:27,260 --> 00:26:28,260
I know.

422
00:26:30,830 --> 00:26:33,530
I've thought about it endlessly.

423
00:26:34,230 --> 00:26:37,500
But to me, my parents are
Kang Nam Bong and Han Young Ja.

424
00:26:38,300 --> 00:26:39,470
Just those two.

425
00:26:41,470 --> 00:26:45,610
My mother is Han Young Ja.

426
00:26:45,980 --> 00:26:47,340
Lawyer Han Young Ja.

427
00:26:48,480 --> 00:26:50,780
I have nothing to do
with CEO Chae Hwa Young.

428
00:26:52,950 --> 00:26:54,220
Does that answer your question?

429
00:26:57,050 --> 00:26:58,790
So you won't even think of anyone else.

430
00:26:59,890 --> 00:27:01,520
That's how happy I'll make you, Jang Mi.

431
00:27:04,730 --> 00:27:06,000
Happiness is a luxury I can't afford.

432
00:27:07,860 --> 00:27:09,530
All I have left is revenge.

433
00:27:34,620 --> 00:27:35,730
You can go now.

434
00:27:36,090 --> 00:27:37,190
Just lie down for a bit.

435
00:27:37,790 --> 00:27:38,800
I'm fine.

436
00:27:39,930 --> 00:27:42,530
Come on. Lie down.

437
00:27:42,570 --> 00:27:45,700
- Just leave me alone, please.
- For goodness' sake.

438
00:27:46,370 --> 00:27:48,370
- Get some rest.
- Yes.

439
00:28:20,170 --> 00:28:21,170
I'm sorry.

440
00:28:21,700 --> 00:28:23,140
I'm so sorry, Baek Ho.

441
00:28:24,370 --> 00:28:27,910
You are the most wonderful first man
in my life.

442
00:28:29,080 --> 00:28:32,450
My love, forever alive in my heart.

443
00:28:57,210 --> 00:28:58,880
(The First Man)

444
00:28:58,940 --> 00:29:01,480
Chairman, what's that emblem
on the cutlery?

445
00:29:01,580 --> 00:29:04,150
I hear it's the Chairman's family crest.

446
00:29:04,210 --> 00:29:05,320
Baek Ho.

447
00:29:05,520 --> 00:29:08,850
Don't waver, Oh Jang Mi.
Do you want Baek Ho to get hurt again?

448
00:29:09,020 --> 00:29:10,920
This is even harder than revenge.

449
00:29:11,520 --> 00:29:14,490
Today is the last day.
I won't say goodbye in tears.

450
00:29:14,760 --> 00:29:16,290
I'm doing this for his happiness.

451
00:29:16,430 --> 00:29:17,930
I had a wonderful time.

452
00:29:17,930 --> 00:29:20,100
Goodbye, my first man.

453
00:29:21,160 --> 00:29:23,170
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
